                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="row review-item">
                                    <div class="col-xs-3 review-number"><ins>9.0</ins> <span>Isbawandi Zin</span> <small>from London, UK, 3/2/ 2014</small></div>
                                    <div class="col-xs-9 review-text">
